These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, iris
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, lime
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike
1. the person eating kiwi is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Flower         | iris   | amaryllis |
| Food   | kiwi | lime    |
| Transport     | helicopter  | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-2::.
City: boston, hamburg
2 different pets are kept: rabbit, fish
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the jet-ski is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| City      | hamburg    | boston    |
| Pet   | rabbit | fish    |
| Transport     | jet-ski  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-3::.
House: craftsman, modern
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, musical
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, french
1. the craftsman house is not to the right of the french##8
2. the person watching musical movies is not the french##6
3. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |        2        |
| House      | craftsman   | modern           |
| Movie-Genre           | thriller | musical |
| Nationality   | french  | australian      |

