.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, superhero
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, emerald
1. the person who likes emerald is not to the right of the person watching superhero movies##8
2. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person watching superhero movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |
| Movie-Genre       | superhero  | comedy   |
| Sport       | lacrosse | parkour |
| Color   | emerald    | amber |

