.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-8-10::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, sailing
The people have 2 different hobbies: cooking, video-games
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##8
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person driving the car##1
3. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |  2   |
| Sport        | sailing | biathlon |
| Hobby         | video-games     | cooking |
| Transport   | motorbike   | car  |

