There are 2 different nationalities: french, german
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the french##1
2. the game-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the game-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Pet           | goldfish | lizard   |
| Cigar   | game | bluemaster |
| Nationality   | french  | german  |

